      <h2 style="text-align: center;">Introduction</h2>
      <p class="blocktext">After having been sent an image which showed an ancient Sumerian tablet containing someone's complaint about the delivery of a wrong type of a copper by a friend of mine, I decided to write something in the same vain as that, just in Ancient Greek.</p>
    </div>
